formatted_address: 88 Tanglin Halt Rd, #01-09 Commonwealth View, Singapore 141088
name: Long John Silver's

reviews.text:
Ordered the new buffalo single fish burger set. As u can see in the pic, is one soggy mess. Do not expect much when hot sauce and wet coleslaw on crispy fish. Taste wasn't bad tho. If you like mushy bread on mushy fish with mushy vegetables. The fries are good though.

AC is almost non-existent . It is not even crowded. There's only 2 of us customers in the shop. Is that why they do not bother to turn on the AC?

Bad food, bad service, bad atmosphere.

Fries were cold and fish was dry. When we returned the food, the replacement was sent to our table in less than 5minutes time and they simply mixed in some hot fries and the fish was still as dry.

Air-con wasn’t working, and Coke weren’t gassy. I am never going to dine there anymore.

ordered via delivery, horrible experience. please don't waste your money they never get their orders right and you get wrong orders that are way less than what you paid for. i got sides instead of the mains i orederred for, and i did not even purchase porridge.

food was served cold and hard, fries were lumpy and sticky, place was stuffy and smelly, (no ventilation) in an enclosed area with toilet at the back and frying in the front, mgmt shd do something or else this be the end of ljs i”m afraid

Food and service was great, only the floors needed a little cleaning up
Will come again
